  "description": "Cosmology is the study of the origin, evolution, large-scale structure, and ultimate fate of the universe. It draws on general relativity, thermodynamics, and observational astronomy to construct models of the universe as a whole \u0026ndash; not individual stars or planets, but the geometry and composition of everything at the largest scales.\n",
